title: From Black Youngstas to Latin OGs
itunes:title: From Black Youngstas to Latin OGs
description:
FRI 9/9 - Blac Youngsta chops it up with Envy, Angela & Charlamagne about his new mixtape "F Everybody", being signed to Yo Gotti, why he ate that Twix in Wal-Mart and how he's done making "young & dumb" mistakes. Then the hip-hop legend N.O.R.E. stops by The Breakfast Club to discuss the success of his "Drink Champs" podcast, his job as hip-hop's beef squasher and what went wrong when 2 Chainz WENT OFF on Jack Thriller.
